         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Premier's Office ¶ Melbourne 17th March 1897 ¶ Dear Sir. ¶  ¶ With reference to the case of the late Baron Von Mueller the Premier desires me to say that the Cabinet has decided to grant 9 (nine) mont...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M97.03.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Robert Rogers to William Potter</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">E98/10135, unit 972, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS headed 'Copy of reply sent to Revd Mr Potter'.</p>
               </note>Premier's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 17th March 1897</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to the case of the late Baron Von Mueller the Premier desires me to say that the Cabinet has decided to grant 9 (nine) months pay as a gratuity; to be paid to the Executors at once.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Government will also if requested by the Memorial Committee contribute towards the expense of a monument on the Baron's grave to a reasonable amount.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours faithfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(sd) Robert S Rogers</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary to the Premier</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Revd W. Potter</p>
            <p rend="letter"
